emplate message permira type limited liability partnership industry private equity growth capital founded   years ago  headquarters london united kingdom products leveraged buyout aum € billion number of employees  website wwwpermiracom permira is a european private equity firm founded in  the firm advises funds with a total committed capital of approximately € billion since  the permira funds raised from pension funds and other institutions have made nearly  private equity investments permira specialises in five sectors consumer financial services healthcare industrials and tmt technology media telecommunications there are currently  companies in the permira funds’ portfolio and the firm comprises approximately  professionals contents  history  recent investments  recent realisations  current investments  references  external links historyedit permira was founded in  by nicholas ferguson as a number of countryspecific separate businesses operating under the schroder ventures brand in  the uk french german and italian teams joined together to create schroder ventures europe and in  it raised its first paneuropean fund in  the firm was renamed permira permira opened an office in new york city in  one in tokyo in  and one in hong kong in  it also opened an office in menlo park in  recent investmentsedit   acquisition of medora snacks and ideal snacks medora snacks manufacturers branded betterforyou snacks while ideal is the leading contract manufacturer of betterforyou diversified popped snacks    acquisition of vacalians group a major european campsite and mobilehome company operating under the tohapi brand    acquisition of gfkl financial services a leading provider of receivables management services in germany    acquisition of informatica the worlds number one independent provider of enterprise data integration software and services    acquisition of teraco data environments subsaharan africas leading provider of carrier neutral datacenter services    acquisition 