ading company in premium and luxury segment of the apparel market   arysta lifescience limited one of the worlds largest agrochemical businesses   renaissance learning leading provider of technologybased school improvement and student assessment programmes   allmedia leading creator of tv film and digital content   prosiebensat one of the largest independent media corporations in europe current investmentsedit the permira funds are invested in the following companies atrium innovations leader in the manufacturing development and commercialisation of innovative sciencebased health products  €m cabb integrated supplier of fine and speciality chemicals and customer manufacturing solutions  €m dr martens iconic british footwear brand  €m legal zoom online legal services company  €m pantheon healthcare group formerly mesa and astral  €m metalogix leading provider of online management tools teamviewer global provider of secure remote support software  €m teraco data environment largest provider of carrierneutral datacenter services in subsaharan africa tilney bestinvest formerly bestinvest a leading private client wealth management firm and tilney a wealth manager  €m akindo sushiro sushi restaurant chain japan  €m ancestrycom global leader in online family history  €b asia broadcast satellite premium fixed satellite services operator  €m bakercorp temporary liquid and solid containment pump filtration and trench solutions  €m creganna medical global provider of outsourced solutions to the medical device industry  €m edreams odigeo a combination of a trio of travel companies edreams go voyages and opodo  €m genesys leading supplier of enterprise software and solutions  €m intelligrated automated material handling solutions usa  €m just retirement specialist financial services uk  €m netafim smart drip and micro irrigation solutions israel €m pharmaq world leading aquatic health groups  €m saga acromas financial services to people aged over  in the uk  €m sisal italian gam